The hMPV M gene and hBoV NP1 gene from 13 samples were amplified and sequenced. The phylogenetic analysis of the hBoV nucleotide sequences revealed that all hBoV strains clustered with the hBoV1 (NC_007455) genotype (identity range 75.0–100%) (Fig. 2
). The hMPV strains belonged to the A2 subgroup (identity range 74.0–97.0%) (Fig. 3
).
